{"talk":{"id":26076,"name":"Rachel Wurzman: How isolation fuels opioid addiction","description":"What do Tourette syndrome, heroin addiction and social media obsession all have in common? They converge in an area of the brain called the striatum, says neuroscientist Rachel Wurzman -- and this critical discovery could reshape our understanding of the opioid crisis. Sharing insights from her research, Wurzman shows how social isolation contributes to relapse and overdose rates and reveals how meaningful human connection could offer a potentially powerful source of recovery.","slug":"rachel_wurzman_how_isolation_fuels_opioid_addiction","recorded_at":"2017-10-27 00:00:00","published_at":"2018-10-29 14:48:14","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:44:14","viewed_count":1403445,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":120,"name":"TEDxMidAtlantic"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/17515ea69048c09be4f374a86a5c50dcd531d0a6_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/17515ea69048c09be4f374a86a5c50dcd531d0a6_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/17515ea69048c09be4f374a86a5c50dcd531d0a6_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/17515ea69048c09be4f374a86a5c50dcd531d0a6_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/9f1e9b0aeba57e0b529afbc82a4bc10a019e00b3_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/RachelWurzman_2017X-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":9129473,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/RachelWurzman_2017X-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":25357372,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/RachelWurzman_2017X-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":44825542,"